Tom Daley felt inferior because of his sexuality
Olympic jumper Tom Daley says he grew up feeling inferior to others because of his sexuality, though this was, in turn, what motivated him to become a winner.
At 24, she told us that it wasn't until she was in high school that she realized that "not everyone was like me".
